content: Works great and easy to script paths for the Tello. I like the functional UI that is easy to use and logical.  Some suggestions for the future:  1. It was not obvious but the numerical values are clickable buttons. When you click them that step is inserted into the sequence. Please make these UI elements more obvious.  2. I am not sure if it is a limitation of Tello firmware but can the hover duration be increased?  3. A big Red button to stop the script and land immediately would be great in case the flight plan goes awry :)

App is easy to use but unfortunately it keep crashing on my samsung A7 even 
after rebooting it and shutting down any apps running and in airplane mode 
leaving the drone hovering in one place
replyContent: Please be sure bt is on before starting the app. you don't need to put the phone in aero mode as there is no video feed available. app searches for BT on so if you turn it off it crashes

content: Only reason 4 not 5 stars is no Take photo or Start/Stop video. Hope they are included in next release. Otherwise a great app!
replyContent: Hello Jim.  Unfortunaltely Ryze does not allow the video streaming while in command mode. there is actually no chance to have video together with command mode. It belongs to Ryze decisions. If they will allow that, it will surely be implemented.
